{"title":"Hexo集成gitalk评论区配置-aurora主题","uid":"36a2486607108757adb270ce5bdb8003","slug":"博客-gitalk配置","date":"2023-09-08T13:38:20.000Z","updated":"2023-09-09T02:00:44.880Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/博客-gitalk配置.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/随笔配图/R-C.57b10qgfzps0.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"Hexo框架\"><a href=\"#Hexo框架\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo框架\"></a>Hexo框架</h2><p>Hexo框架的使用教程挺多的了，根据以下两个链接，足以正常搭建和使用。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/guide/\">Hexo官方中文文档</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yishuihean.cn/post/hexo-aurora-github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\">hexo+aurora+github+gitalk搭建属于自己的个人博客</a></p>\n<p>但两个教程中都未对gitalk的配置展开描述，此教程旨在记录gitalk的配置流程。</p>\n<h2 id=\"Gitalk功能\"><a href=\"#Gitalk功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Gitalk功能\"></a>Gitalk功能</h2><ul>\n<li>可作为Hexo框架下的插件，为博客提供评论区功能</li>\n<li>使用Github账号登录后方可评论</li>\n<li>评论存储在Github仓库的issue中</li>\n<li>支持无干扰模式(distractionFreeMode: true)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Gitalk官方网址\"><a href=\"#Gitalk官方网址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Gitalk官方网址\"></a>Gitalk官方网址</h2><p>官方网址： <a href=\"https://gitalk.github.io/\">https://gitalk.github.io</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Gitalk配置流程\"><a href=\"#Gitalk配置流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Gitalk配置流程\"></a>Gitalk配置流程</h2><p>1.在Github上注册新应用，链接：<a href=\"https://github.com/settings/applications/new\">https://github.com/settings/applications/new</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94%E9%85%8D%E5%9B%BE/download.5l9e3zliiwk0.webp\"></p>\n<p>URL链接格式 <a href=\"https://xxxx.github.io/\">https://XXXX.github.io</a> ，记得需要加上https:&#x2F;&#x2F;</p>\n<p>2.注册之后会进入如下界面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94%E9%85%8D%E5%9B%BE/image.3i43d429s9e0.webp\"></p>\n<p>点击生成<strong>client secret</strong>，注意client secret在之后将不可见，尽量复制保存至本地。<strong>client ID</strong>和<strong>client secret</strong>之后需要填入主题的配置文件当中。</p>\n<p>3.修改aurora主题_config.aurora.yml配置文件中的gitalk相关选项</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">gitalk:\n  enable: true\n  autoExpand: true\n  clientID: &#39;xxxxx&#39; \n  clientSecret: &#39;xxxxxxxxx&#39;\n  repo: &#39;xxxxxx&#39; ## dev-blo-comments\n  owner: &#39;moonlightleaf&#39; ## owner name\n  admin: [&#39;moonlightleaf&#39;] ## [&#39;admin_name&#39;]\n  id: uid\n  language: cn\n  distractionFreeMode: true\n  recentComment: true\n  proxy: &#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>需要填入上一步生成的<strong>client ID</strong>和<strong>client secret</strong>，并填入仓库名，将自己的github用户名设置为owner和admin，别的选项无需修改。最后的proxy选项可以自行设置反向代理，方便国内用户访问（国内用户被墙，可能出现network error的错误提示）。我是魔法常驻用户，因此就没有设置反向代理。</p>\n<p>4.执行命令，重新生成并发布，刷新博客就能看到评论区啦。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo clean &amp; hexo g &amp; hexo d</code></pre>\n\n<p>gitalk貌似在本地测试环境中不能用，因此必须hexo d命令发布后，才能看到评论区。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Hexo框架Hexo框架的使用教程挺多的了，根据以下两个链接，足以正常搭建和使用。 Hexo官方中文文档 hexo+aurora+github+gitalk搭建...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"博客搭建","slug":"博客搭建","count":2,"path":"api/categories/博客搭建.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"博客搭建","slug":"博客搭建","count":2,"path":"api/tags/博客搭建.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hexo%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hexo框架</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Gitalk%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gitalk功能</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Gitalk%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%BD%91%E5%9D%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gitalk官方网址</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Gitalk%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gitalk配置流程</span></a>